# 🛣️ JavaScript Roadmap: Beginner to Advanced

A complete guide to mastering JavaScript from scratch — designed for web developers, learners, and aspiring software engineers.

---

## ✅ Prerequisites

- Basic understanding of **HTML** and **CSS**
- Familiarity with using the **browser console**

---

## 🟢 1. Beginner Level – Core JavaScript

### 📚 Topics

- What is JavaScript?
- Variables: `var`, `let`, `const`
- Data Types: string, number, boolean, null, undefined
- Operators: arithmetic, comparison, logical
- Control Structures: `if`, `else`, `switch`, `for`, `while`
- Functions (declaration, expression, arrow functions)
- Arrays and Objects
- Basic DOM Manipulation
- Event Handling: `onclick`, `onchange`

### 💻 Projects

- Quote Generator
- To-Do List
- Color Flipper
- Simple Calculator

---

## 🟡 2. Intermediate Level – DOM + ES6+

### 📚 Topics

- DOM Traversal
- Events: `addEventListener`, bubbling, delegation
- `setTimeout`, `setInterval`
- Callback Functions
- ES6+ Features:
  - Template literals
  - Destructuring
  - Spread/Rest operators
  - Optional chaining
- Array Methods: `map`, `filter`, `reduce`, `find`, `forEach`
- Object Manipulation
- LocalStorage & SessionStorage
- Error Handling: `try`, `catch`, `finally`

### 💻 Projects

- Quiz App
- Notes App (LocalStorage)
- Expense Tracker
- Countdown Timer

---

## 🔵 3. Advanced Level – Async & OOP

### 📚 Topics

- Promises & `async/await`
- Fetch API & JSON
- Closures
- Scope, Hoisting, Execution Context
- `this`, `bind`, `call`, `apply`
- Prototypes & Prototype Inheritance
- Classes & Object-Oriented Programming
- JavaScript Modules (import/export)
- Event Loop

### 💻 Projects

- Weather App (API)
- GitHub Profile Finder
- Movie Search App (OMDb API)
- Real-time Chat UI (frontend only)

---

## 🔴 4. Expert Level – Performance, Patterns, & Tooling

### 📚 Topics

- Functional Programming (FP)
- Memoization, Currying
- Debounce & Throttle
- JavaScript Design Patterns (Factory, Observer, etc.)
- Web Workers & Service Workers
- WebSockets
- Testing (Jest/Mocha)
- Tooling: Vite, Webpack, Babel
- Linting: ESLint, Prettier
- TypeScript Basics

### 💻 Projects

- AI Chatbot UI (w/ Hugging Face API)
- Collaborative Notes App (IndexedDB)
- Real-time Whiteboard (Socket.io)
- Resume Builder App
- Portfolio Website with Theme Switcher

---

## 🚀 Bonus Topics (2025 & Beyond)

- AI Integration (OpenAI, Hugging Face, LangChain.js)
- WebXR and WebAR (3D and VR/AR with JS)
- Electron.js or Tauri for desktop apps
- React, Vue, Svelte (pick one framework to master)
- Charting with D3.js or Chart.js
- JS Security: XSS, CSRF, CSP

---

## 🧪 Practice Platforms

| Platform                                     | Use Case                       |
| -------------------------------------------- | ------------------------------ |
| [Codewars](https://codewars.com)             | JavaScript DSA & algorithms    |
| [Frontend Mentor](https://frontendmentor.io) | UI/UX and frontend challenges  |
| [LeetCode](https://leetcode.com)             | Data structures and algorithms |
| [Scrimba](https://scrimba.com)               | Interactive coding courses     |
| [DevDocs](https://devdocs.io)                | All-in-one JS documentation    |

---

## 📝 Learning Tips

- 🔁 Practice by rebuilding projects using new techniques
- 🧠 Read open-source code on GitHub
- ✍️ Blog what you learn on [Dev.to](https://dev.to) or [Hashnode](https://hashnode.com)
- 🚀 Join hackathons or build your own product
- 📁 Maintain a **JavaScript Projects Portfolio** (hosted on Netlify or Vercel)

---

